OL,3,CCafe slams rude customers who use
OL,4,Claptops and eat their own food
OL,6,FThe owners of a coffee shop have
OL,7,Fcriticised rude customers and are
OL,8,Fbanning the use of laptops on their
OL,9,Fground floor.
OL,11,FThe venue is also reminding their
OL,12,Fclientele not to eat food they have
OL,13,Fbought elsewhere after one customer
OL,14,Ftried to eat a whole family-sized
OL,15,Ftiramisu.
OL,17,FCoffi, on Pilgrim Street in the
OL,18,FGeorgian Quarter, in Liverpool shared
OL,19,Fa statement on Instagram, saying:
OL,20,F"From today, laptops are welcome only
OL,21,Fon the laptop bar upstairs.
