OL,3,CCafe slams rude customers who use
OL,4,Claptops and eat their own food
OL,6,F"We've never been able to accommodate
OL,7,Fthem downstairs, or on every table
OL,8,Fupstairs - our space is simply too
OL,9,Fsmall, and we can't afford to turn
OL,10,Faway groups of people because one or
OL,11,Ftwo laptops occupy a table for hours.
OL,13,F"As we continue to grow, it's vital
OL,14,Fthat we balance the needs of customers
OL,15,Fcoming to enjoy coffee with those
OL,16,Fneeding a space to work."
