OL,3,CCafe slams rude customers who use
OL,4,Claptops and eat their own food
OL,6,FThe independent business asked
OL,7,Fcustomers to be nice to their team in
OL,8,Ftheir statement, revealing that some
OL,9,Fpeople have been "extremely rude"
OL,10,Fabout their laptop policy.
OL,12,FCoffi also added that customers who
OL,13,Fbring in their own food and drink will
OL,14,Fbe asked to put it away or leave,
OL,15,Frevealing: "someone tried to eat an
OL,16,Fentire family-sized tiramisu upstairs
OL,17,Fonce.
OL,19,F"You won't outdo that - no point
OL,20,Ftrying!"
